title: Jussie Smollett  Interview and more

description:
Wednesday 5/16 - Today on the show we had actor and now director Jussie Smollet in the building where he spoke about his characters influence on Empire, new music and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a woman that was accused of sending 65,000 text messages after a first date. Moreover, Angela gave some advice to to some listeners during "Ask Yee".
